name: mapping-mode为vlan_pri
description:
mapping-mode is vlan_pri ,config gem mapping vlan 2000 +pri2
    测试方法：上下行各发送两条流：vlan2000 pri2和 vlan2000 pri3 ；发送vlan 2001 pri2
    结果：vlan 2000 pri2的上下行都能通；vlan2000 pri3下行能通，vlan2000 pri3上行不通;vlan 2001上下行都不通
